                </blockquote>
                <div class="profile-circle" style="background-color: rgba(0,0,0,.2);"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="item">
                <blockquote>
                    <p>Many diseases today are of unknown source (or not well defined) For example: fungi in the mouth, migraines and fibromyalgia. There is not a large enough database that will help physicians to better investigate the nature of diseases and their etiology.</p>
